{"tid":2350369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要撐 香港電台大事回顧係痴撚線高質","createTime":"2021-01-02T08:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T10:13:09.000Z","uid":154903,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"63723cc6af6b7bc6c2fa4fa241320fee53c26f67","tid":2350369,"uid":154903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYd4i1E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYd4i1E.png&h=3ef48ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台身為香港嘅公共廣播機構，今年已經有記者被狗咬。<br />\n下年員工亦都要宣誓效宗，即係話今年係佢地最後一年可以憑唔使被效忠嘅良心做節目，今次佢地去到盡，大家要諗辦法撐。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台監製話：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthkPCA/posts/1835297316617839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FrthkPCA%2Fposts%2F1835297316617839&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb07y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=fb1a7aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthkPCA/posts/1835297316617839</a><br />\n<br />\n《回顧大事回顧》<br />\n大事回顧是為一年定調的工作。大家看的是短短26分鐘，背後卻是導演金精火眼回顧365天新聞的拼勁。當中有海量的人物「金句」要挑選，上千計小時的畫面逐格推敲；報導不僅要呈現2020的大格局，也要刻劃觸動人心的事件細節，付上的可算是「懷疑人生級」的努力。<br />\n而且，這一年 - 香港二次回歸「元年」，下筆特別難。 世事紛亂，世人看法極端，禁語紅線處處，遣詞用句難免比以往更感如履薄冰。有天閒聊時，主持利君雅說，2020是失語呀 。奈何我們的職責就是要「記史」， 總得要在短短26分鐘中，將2020的「失語」，從混沌、矛盾中刻劃出來。<br />\n有人說，今年表達手法很「文青」，這格調並不是刻意的，只是想表達的東西剛好比較文藝而已，難道今年不是多了人重拾寫信嗎？<br />\n不過，放「詩句」確是文青而很少在時事節目中出現的。<br />\n2020，明明需要擁抱，偏偏卻要隔離。構思時想到除了給觀眾分析時勢大局，還希望在崩緊情緒中，留下一丁點安慰。<br />\n年輕詩人為節目寫了很多動人字句，在節目中有播出或沒播出，現在給大家一次送上。<br />\n今集也是港台編導、監製在宣誓前最後一次製作的大事回顧，2021將會是怎樣的光景？<br />\n在齊太史簡，在晉董狐筆。我們正正對時代忠誠，才希望記錄一切。<br />\nP.S. 給製作團隊：和你 奮鬥我很愉快<br />\n監製  徐岱靈<br />\n《2020香港政情大事回顧》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9nQs582IBdM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9nQs582IBdM&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb07y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=602d7271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9nQs582IBdM</a><br />\n《2020國際風雲大事回顧》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YpW_qpx2cdk&amp;t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYpW_qpx2cdk%26t%3D2s&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb07y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=a82f27bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YpW_qpx2cdk&amp;t=2s</a>"},{"pid":"8e56f2f42b63fc9bb72fde7a84b05104f1363955","tid":2350369,"uid":154903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WijSnt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WijSnt.png&h=b0425629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cL78LHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcL78LHu.jpg&h=75519a6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7d40bab70e1cda985c82cd19633df909e348fcc","tid":2350369,"uid":43062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"港台CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458ef5a1b2861631e58450be7e24d184e1bf91d0","tid":2350369,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"4dc1a83fe37e9a03da7c22e7c18b61b3cf41e1fb","tid":2350369,"uid":4629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"大家一齊撐住港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7283cccab81440e3f67357f78d328be864798c93","tid":2350369,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75187b7d6080471b16de3cc41bbd4b11b7581963","tid":2350369,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69dfc4d108bef697bb9a6ee2e5